comments: Prof. Schlossman loves what she does. If you need her help she\'s there for you and even offers office time. Most of the work is done on computers and she makes it interesting and interactive. She\'s even allows you to call her by her first name. If you failed this class, you might as well rethink what you want to do in life because she\'s an easy A.
She\'s an excellent professor, I really loved digital design with her. She\'s very helpful and understanding, and a great teacher too!

SHe is a very nice sweet person, who asks that you attend class to keep up and get a good grade. Took her Dig. Photo class and learned about photoshop and functions of a camera. Enjoyed the fieldtrip we took to take nature pics! Def. Recommend her!

SHe is a very nice sweet person, who asks that you attend class to keep up and get a good grade. Took her Dig. Photo class and learned about photoshop and functions of a camera. Enjoyed the fieldtrip we took to take nature pics! Def. Recommend her!

She is an incredible teacher. She has a wealth of knowledge and is very encouraging. I have taken 2 classes with her, digital and B&W photography, and would take more classes with her if I could. All she asks is that you attend class, and keep up with assignments, and you can get a good grade. Her enthusiasm inspired me to work as hard as possible.

Had her for digital photo. Though I\'d worked with digital cameras before, she taught me many different functions that I wasn\'t familiar with. Very helpful and insightful teacher. All she asks for is for students to keep up with the assignments. Very much recommended.

I had her for b/w photo. I knew nothing about cameras or picture taking before I started, but I\'m learning a lot now. She\'s young, enthusiastic, helpful, and very encouraging. I really recommend her, it\'s a lot of fun!
